title: I have riot kayle, but i cant figure out what skin i got
body:
Hello,
My friends just told me they've got their riot kayle without any notification. Since i have riot kayle already, i went through all my champs looking for a new skin and found nothing.

Did we get the mystery skin yet? If so, can someone help me to find put what skin i ve got.

Thanks!

replies.body:
Idk man, but I'd like to know what I got too xDD
Same situation here, it popped up saying I got a mystery gift and the icon, but didn't show what I got.
Please help, thanks!

> [{quoted}](name=Non Toxic Bleach,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=PegMv7cz,comment-id=0001,timestamp=2016-09-15T19:57:28.815+0000)
>
> Idk man, but I'd like to know what I got too xDD
> Same situation here, it popped up saying I got a mystery gift and the icon, but didn't show what I got.
> Please help, thanks!

im in the same boat as you. I have had riot kayle for being in a special alienware riot tournament for a long time now.
so i have the icon but nothing else.

Looking into this, the account has not received these gifts yet!  Gifts have not finished rolling out, and it may take some time for everything to complete considering the many eligible accounts.  We'll be posting updates through our[ support ticker.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-)  Hang tight!

The Riot Kayle skin + summoner's icon is being released to people across League of Legends in waves, as they say their system doesn't allow them to add it to everyone's account all at once. Therefore, you probably haven't gotten it yet.
